{"tid":1622613,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全部驚咗緊急法嘅人入嚟","createTime":"2019-10-04T16:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T17:07:42.000Z","uid":25686,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"68e66788a730150af78c83609afec7acff447a21","tid":1622613,"uid":25686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:45:35.000Z","msg":"和理非由遊行唔帶口罩，進化到全民口罩<br />\n由譴責佔路，進化到一齊佔領<br />\n由勇武，進化到火魔法<br />\n和理非次次冇不反對通知書都照出<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以我哋都唔會驚咗反蒙面法而唔出嚟</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">前線願意為你擋子彈，香港人願唔願意全民繼續帶口罩</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港人，反抗！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全民口罩，十月六號見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不了，我驚咗林鄭"},{"pid":"a7f2388fb6d46b9aa15f36bbd4f6ab2a47e43163","tid":1622613,"uid":25686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:46:51.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c28bfc4e02c89ae7e01624222ed27f2c86868910","tid":1622613,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:47:39.000Z","msg":"［極重要］做嘢還做嘢，P牌仔想畀個革命方向大家討論討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1621742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1621742</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"803a026a9125b3ff680917e71fec2c5ea44ca80b","tid":1622613,"uid":25686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:47:40.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"a56a3ffe4970d4282d107dcfa1a844e0c2ace20f","tid":1622613,"uid":25686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:48:41.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"0fd66d5af5f125a065220370e4b67f9dc2d6bea5","tid":1622613,"uid":25686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AK6jRrC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAK6jRrC.jpg&h=5e85a927&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c1134